review_classify_user.system_prompt:
研究主题: {research_question}

论文列表（序号即论文标识）:
{papers_text}

请将这些论文按研究主题划分为 3-6 个类别。
每个类别包含：name（类别名称）、description（类别描述）、paper_indices（论文序号列表）。
每篇论文必须且只能归入一个类别。

review_classify_user_en.system_prompt:
Research topic: {research_question}

Paper list (numbers are paper identifiers):
{papers_text}

Classify these papers into 3-6 categories by research theme.
Each category: name, description, paper_indices (list of paper numbers).
Every paper must belong to exactly one category.

review_relationship_user.system_prompt:
主题: {theme_name}
主题描述: {theme_desc}

论文:
{papers_text}

详细分析这些论文之间的逻辑关系。
relationship_type 填最显著的关系类型（演进/对比/互补/并行）。
description 必须逐对说明具体关系（演进/对比/互补）。

review_relationship_user_en.system_prompt:
Theme: {theme_name}
Theme description: {theme_desc}

Papers:
{papers_text}

Analyze the logical relationships among these papers.
relationship_type: the most prominent type (evolution/contrast/complement/parallel).
description: specify relationships between each pair of papers.

review_section_user.system_prompt:
研究主题: {research_question}
本章主题: {theme_name}
主题描述: {theme_desc}
论文间关系: {relationship}

相关论文（引用编号即最终参考文献编号）:
{papers_text}

请撰写该主题的综述内容。
要求：
- 只用连贯段落书写，不要标题、不要分点列表
- 引用使用 [编号]，编号即上面提供的论文编号
- 综合讨论多篇论文，而非逐篇罗列

review_section_user_en.system_prompt:
Research topic: {research_question}
Section theme: {theme_name}
Theme description: {theme_desc}
Paper relationships: {relationship}

Related papers (citation numbers = final reference numbers):
{papers_text}

Write the review content for this theme.
Requirements:
- Flowing paragraphs only, no headings, no bullet points
- Use [number] for citations
- Synthesize multiple papers, don't list them one by one

review_intro_user.system_prompt:
研究主题: {research_question}

包含以下主题:
{themes_overview}

请撰写综述的引言部分。

review_intro_user_en.system_prompt:
Research topic: {research_question}

Themes covered:
{themes_overview}

Write the introduction section.

review_conclusion_user.system_prompt:
研究主题: {research_question}

各章节内容:
{sections_summary}

请撰写综述的总结与展望部分。

review_conclusion_user_en.system_prompt:
Research topic: {research_question}

Section summaries:
{sections_summary}

Write the conclusion and future work section.

review_abstract_user.system_prompt:
标题: {title}

引言摘要:
{intro_preview}

主题章节:
{sections_preview}

总结:
{conclusion_preview}

基于以上内容，撰写一段 200 字以内的摘要，概述综述的目的、方法和主要发现。

review_abstract_user_en.system_prompt:
Title: {title}

Introduction:
{intro_preview}

Theme sections:
{sections_preview}

Conclusion:
{conclusion_preview}

Based on the above, write a 200-word abstract summarizing the purpose, methods, and main findings.

